text: Elvira Becks (born 8 May 1976) is a Dutch gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nijmegen
